  "text": "Sorry to ask the unimportant question. I was thinking of the future readers, and that they would be totally mystified as to how much… Was there a significance with respect to the hawk that landed the other day just outside of the kitchen window? I am Ra. This is correct. We may note that we find it interesting that queries offered to us are often already known. We assume that our confirmation is appreciated.",
